===Etymology 1===
The [[exopassive]] of {{och-l|攘|to remove}} ("to remove" > ("to remove oneself") > "to yield; to concede").

Cognate with {{och-l|攘|to remove; to steal}}, {{och-l|禳|to expel; to sacrifice to expel disasters}}, {{cog|bo|གནང||to give; to grant}}, {{cog|my|နှင်း||to confer; to grant}}, {{cog|my|နှင်||to drive away; to expel}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}); all from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*naŋ|t=to drive; grant, allow}}.

====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[allow]]; to [[let]]; to [[permit]]
#: {{zh-x|媽媽{ma} 不 讓 我 去。|Mum won't '''let''' me go.}}
#: {{zh-x|讓 我們 聯合 一起 把 這 項 工作 做 好。|'''Let''''s team up to get this task finished.}}
# to [[ask]] {{gl|someone to do something}}; to [[get]] {{gl|someone to do something}}; to [[have]] {{gl|someone do something}}
#: {{zh-x|醫生 讓 我 打針。|The doctor told me to get a shot.}}
# to [[yield]]; to [[concede]]
#: {{zh-x|弟弟{di} 還 小，你 就 讓 著{zhe} 他 一點 吧。|Your brother is still little, why don't you just '''let him have his way''' a bit.}}
# {{lb|zh|driving}} to [[yield]]; to [[give way]]
# [[by]] (passive signifier)
#: {{zh-x|行李{li} 讓 雨 給 淋濕 了。|The luggage was soaked '''by''' rain.}}
# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[criticise]]; to [[reproach]]
#* {{zh-x|^夷-吾 訴 之，公 使 讓 之。|Yiwu informed Duke Xian of Jin [of the incident]; the Duke dispatched messengers to '''reprimand''' him (Shi Wei).|ref=Zuozhuan}}

